Subject: Re: [VB] 71 Clutch disk question -Springs or no Springs

Hi John,
If you do not drag race your bus, then the spring centered clutch disc  is 
fine.  This reduces load shock on the tranny and engine and  improves engine 
longevity.  If you drag race any VW use the solid center  clutch disc.
Eric&Barb
